    </programme>
    <programme start="20260628010600 +0800" stop="20260628030600 +0800" channel="245">
      <title>Des Racines &amp;amp; Des Ailes 第1集 -Terroirs Of Excellence In The Provencal Alps</title>
      <desc>From Saint-Paul-de-Vence to the Roya Valley, in the hinterland of Nice, enthusiasts are fighting to promote their territory. By reviving an old perfume house or creating a high-end spirit with small spelt, these artisans are committed to preserving their precious heritage.</desc>
    </programme>
    <programme start="20260628030600 +0800" stop="20260628033300 +0800" channel="245">
      <title>Gotha 第5集 -The New Era Of Royals!</title>
      <desc>Spotlight on Elisabeth, Duchess of Brabant, who, on the eve of her 24th birthday, is redefining royal codes. Also: the enthronement of Guillaume, new Grand Duke of Luxembourg; the princely world reveals its contrasts; traditions, hidden lineages and scandals expose the true face of today&amp;apos;s dynasties.</desc>
    </programme>
    <programme start="20260628033300 +0800" stop="20260628040000 +0800" channel="245">
      <title>CA Pousse Au Fenua 第1季第10集 -Spices Of The Fenua, An Invitation To Travel</title>
      <desc>Some spices arrived in Tahiti by chance, along the routes of travel. Others are grown locally. All of them, in any case, play a major role in local cuisine and in recipes passed down from generation to generation.</desc>
    </programme>
    <programme start="20260628040000 +0800" stop="20260628042700 +0800" channel="245">
      <title>Passe-Moi Les Jumelles 第14季第4集 -Wendy&amp;apos;s Ark</title>
      <desc>Wendy Pichard heads La Bouche qui rit, the first refuge for farm animals in French speaking Switzerland. Pigs, horses, donkeys, goats, sheep... With her team, she rescues and cares for abused animals or those destined for slaughter.</desc>
    </programme>
    <programme start="20260628042700 +0800" stop="20260628045700 +0800" channel="245">
      <title>Cuisine Ouverte 第16集 -In Sceaux, With Francois Alu</title>
      <desc>Mory Sacko is at Parc de Sceaux with etoile dancer Francois Alu. On today&amp;apos;s menu: a shakshuka.</desc>
    </programme>
