    </programme>
    <programme start="20260628052300 +0800" stop="20260628054800 +0800" channel="245">
      <title>Le Beau Velo De Ravel 第7集 -Peruwelz</title>
      <desc>Peruwelz, in the Tournaisis region: a rich stop, well worth a visit for its many green and architectural assets. The town, crossed by two canals, is home to many treasures: the Basilica of Our Lady of Bon-Secours, numerous castles and mansions, the Escaut Plains Nature Park.</desc>
    </programme>
    <programme start="20260628054800 +0800" stop="20260628061400 +0800" channel="245">
      <title>Paname 第9集 -Paname Takes The Plunge</title>
      <desc>Paris was built around the Seine: its streets are numbered according to their position in relation to the river. Its coat of arms and motto, &amp;apos;Fluctuat nec mergitur&amp;apos;, refer to water. Immerse yourself in this major element of Parisian life.</desc>
    </programme>
