      <title>Chroniques Mediterraneennes Nature 第1集 -The Pre-Alps</title>
      <desc>Created in 2012 to ensure its preservation and sustainable development, the Prealpes d&amp;apos;Azur Regional Nature Park covers ninety thousand hectares. Its wide-ranging altitude and its dual climate, Alpine and Mediterranean, have shaped exceptional landscapes. Today, it is recognized as a global biodiversity hotspot.</desc>
