      <desc>It is a jewel with the look of a Grand Canyon. 250 million years ago, the volcanic massif of the Esterel separated from Africa when the Mediterranean was forming. Between Cannes and Saint-Tropez, the Esterel covers the south-east of the Var and extends into the Alpes-Maritimes. Cliffs, forests, sea, its landscapes are astonishing...</desc>
